Package: tramvs
Type: Package
Title: Optimal Subset Selection for Transformation Models
Version: 0.0-1
Authors@R: c(person("Lucas", "Kook", email = "lucasheinrich.kook@uzh.ch", 
    role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Sandra", "Siegfried", role = "ctb"),
    person("Torsten", "Hothorn", role = "ctb"))
Description: Greedy optimal subset selection for transformation models 
    <doi:10.1111/sjos.12291> based on the abess algorithm 
    <doi:10.1073/pnas.2014241117>. Applicable to models from packages
    tram and cotram.
